Brief

The "Dell Technologies World 2023" app is your digital portal to one of the most anticipated technology events of the year, hosted by Dell. This app serves as a comprehensive guide, providing attendees with essential information to navigate the event, connect with others, and maximize their conference experience. Whether you're attending in person or virtually, this app is designed to give you a seamless and informative event journey.
